She ran after DarkMouse.  She almost caugh up with her.
"Hey, quit running.  I'm here to help.  Geez, don't you recognize me?"

DarkMouse:
With her pet rat in her mouth, "No I don'd. I neffer shaw you before 
in my life. Leafe me alone!"  She put on some extra speed and bolted 
forward.

STOP!"

She kept right on running. With a wolf right behind her.
